    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/f915b324a32eca82c1c01b3bd939775f.avif?t=1749338689\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras_big/f915b324a32eca82c1c01b3bd939775f.avif?t=1749338689 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the breathtaking world of <i>Limitless (&quot;Formerly known as Apeiron&quot;)</i>, an open-world, third-person, story-driven action RPG set in the mystical Realm of Eternity. Experience a richly crafted high-fantasy universe filled with danger, discovery, and dynamic gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/5dcd2d1c77f947c04f9becfe45f0f536.webp?t=1749338689\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Dream Team of Heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead a squad of four remarkable companions, each with their own strengths, skills, and customizable gear. Strategically swap between characters in real-time to overcome challenges, solve mysteries, and turn the tide of battle in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/8efc7ad19ce50c6375ccc5c65c5c0add.poster.avif?t=1749338689\" width=786 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/8efc7ad19ce50c6375ccc5c65c5c0add.webm?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/8efc7ad19ce50c6375ccc5c65c5c0add.mp4?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Master the Art of Combat with Weapon Stances </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Revolutionize your battles with our cutting-edge weapon stance system. Instantly switch between powerful combat styles to counter enemies, adapt to changing battlefields, and unleash devastating attacks that will leave your foes in awe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/a3c6a15947b11e660ab0653549970350.poster.avif?t=1749338689\" width=726 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/a3c6a15947b11e660ab0653549970350.webm?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/a3c6a15947b11e660ab0653549970350.mp4?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer Puzzles with Elemental Power</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage your mind and creativity with clever puzzles that demand mastery of the elements. Unlock hidden paths, discover ancient treasures, and bring light to the darkest corners of the Realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/471d63a82d0f797733ac27b6d62d354c.poster.avif?t=1749338689\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/471d63a82d0f797733ac27b6d62d354c.webm?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/471d63a82d0f797733ac27b6d62d354c.mp4?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash the Power of Dynamic Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience combat like never before with fluid, multi-layered mechanics that allow for limitless creativity. Harness the power of elemental abilities, devastating combos, and unique strategies to dominate your enemies and carve your own path to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/e4cf8fed1a1a4b0af37117c058ae4cc4.poster.avif?t=1749338689\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/e4cf8fed1a1a4b0af37117c058ae4cc4.webm?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/e4cf8fed1a1a4b0af37117c058ae4cc4.mp4?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/78a7a8a340ad7771b91c515bf51bf2d5.poster.avif?t=1749338689\" width=800 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/78a7a8a340ad7771b91c515bf51bf2d5.webm?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/78a7a8a340ad7771b91c515bf51bf2d5.mp4?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/17db24edf0ed21135e1434ad3f9d2bfc.poster.avif?t=1749338689\" width=800 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/17db24edf0ed21135e1434ad3f9d2bfc.webm?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/17db24edf0ed21135e1434ad3f9d2bfc.mp4?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/5dcd2d1c77f947c04f9becfe45f0f536.webp?t=1749338689\" width=600 height=22 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dive into a Decade of Legendary Storytelling</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a tale of epic proportions, meticulously crafted over ten years. Follow Dayton, the wielder of an ancient relic, as he battles the interdimensional Ravi army and uncovers the secrets of the Elemental Crystal Fragments in a race to save the Realm from total annihilation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/c5ca54709556b09c1e4043158bb153ce.poster.avif?t=1749338689\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/c5ca54709556b09c1e4043158bb153ce.webm?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/c5ca54709556b09c1e4043158bb153ce.mp4?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/15b7782f31da4067c9a847ec472ee4cc.poster.avif?t=1749338689\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/15b7782f31da4067c9a847ec472ee4cc.webm?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/15b7782f31da4067c9a847ec472ee4cc.mp4?t=1749338689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Journey Awaits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The once-peaceful Realm of Eternity stands on the brink of destruction. As Dayton, forge alliances with warriors, politicians, and cultural icons to challenge the Ravi and reclaim the world’s destiny. The ultimate battle looms in the fabled Garden of Eden—will you be the hero who restores balance?</p>",
